w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/carlos-ibanez-644X6zmy1Hk-unsplash-scaled.jpg 1702w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 681px) 100vw, 681px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-9917a3a\" data-id=\"9917a3a\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-470add2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"470add2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"980\" height=\"550\" src=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-1024x575.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-11017\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-1024x575.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-300x168.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-768x431.jpg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-1536x862.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-2048x1149.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-802x450.jpg 802w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7185a41 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7185a41\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-601ade9 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"601ade9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6535e45 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6535e45\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary Overview<\/h3>\n<p><b>Day 1: Casablanca Arrival<br><\/b>Visit the famous Hassan II Mosque, one of the largest mosques in the world. Explore the stunning architecture and breathtaking ocean views.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 2: Fes<br><\/b>Guided tour of Fes, including historical sites such as the Merenid Tombs, the University of al-Karaouine, and the famous Fes el-Bali medina.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 3: Fes to Merzouga (Sahara Desert)<br><\/b>Drive through Ifrane and Erfoud on your way to the Merzouga Desert. Enjoy a camel trek into the dunes and an unforgettable night in a luxury desert camp.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 4: Rissani &amp; Ait Ouzzine<br><\/b>Visit the historic town of Rissani, famous for its local souks. Then, head to the Berber village of Ait Ouzzine to experience traditional culture. Overnight in Nkob.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 5: A Day with the Berbers<br><\/b>Learn how to bake traditional Berber bread, Bourafin, and enjoy a hands-on experience with the locals. Afterward, travel to Ouarzazate through scenic landscapes.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 6: Ouarzazate &amp; Ait Benhaddou<br><\/b>Visit the UNESCO World Heritage site of Ait Benhaddou and the famous Kasbah Telouet. Continue to Marrakech, with a stop at an Argan cooperative for a local experience.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 7: Marrakech City Tour<br><\/b>Explore the iconic sites of Marrakech, including the Majorelle Gardens, Bahia Palace, Koutoubia Mosque, and the bustling Djemaa El Fna square.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 8: Optional Excursions<br><\/b>Choose between an excursion to the High Atlas Mountains or the Ourika Valley, each offering stunning views and cultural experiences.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 9: Departure<br><\/b>Travel back to Casablanca or Marrakech for your departure, concluding an unforgettable Moroccan journey.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>9-Day Morocco Adventure: From Casablanca to Casablanca Experience the real Morocco with Authentic Berber Travel! This 9-day trip takes you through Morocco&#8217;s rich culture, stunning landscapes, and vibrant cities, starting and ending in Casablanca. Itinerary Overview Day 1: Casablanca ArrivalVisit the famous Hassan II Mosque, one of the largest mosques in the world. Explore the [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11314,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11647","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11647","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11647"}],"version-history":[{"count":20,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11647\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12803,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11647\/revisions\/12803"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11314"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11647"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}